<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR" data-theme="dark">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
<title>Erro no servidor — Padel Experience</title>
{# Deliberately self-contained: no layout extend and no settings/DB reads,
   so this page still renders when the database layer is the thing that failed. #}
<link rel="icon" href="/img/app-logo-positive.svg">
<script>
// Apply the saved/preferred theme before first paint to avoid a dark flash.
(function(){try{var t=localStorage.getItem('px-theme')||(matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: light)').matches?'light':'dark');document.documentElement.dataset.theme=t}catch(e){}})();
</script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/site.css">
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <section class="shell section">
    <div class="empty">
      <div>
        <div class="empty-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 8v4.5M12 15.5h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Algo saiu do lugar.</h3>
        <p>O servidor encontrou um erro ao montar esta página. Costuma ser passageiro — tente de novo em instantes.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/">Voltar ao início</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
